reviewText: She loved it...it was a Birthday present for a 10 year old...and she loved the Movies. thank you very much
I bought this for my mom, took way too long to get it, then it didn't work. It would be a hassle to return and I found it for 7 bucks less at  target. Never again.
National Velvet, Story of Seabiscuit,Black Beauty --- All great movies for a "horse loving" granddaughter!

The movies National Velvet/The Story of Seabiscuit are so full of life and the acting of both Elizabeth Taylor and Mickey Rooney are excellent (in the first film). Shirley Temple excells in the second film. Through the innocense of children, we see these wonderful movies on horse racing.
